{"tid":751783,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"都唔知自己係生存定生活緊","createTime":"2018-07-22T07:36:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-22T11:50:24.000Z","uid":74629,"like":72,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"5e4271136376d90c713cded2cccec58eda6957c8","tid":751783,"uid":74629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T07:36:00.000Z","msg":"日日淨係得返工放工<br />\n一放左工就攰到仆街<br />\n唔係身體肌肉攰嗰種，係精神上好撚攰<br />\n攰到返到屋企都唔想郁，食飽飯淨係想攤喺度<br />\n要去做gym? 不了，聽日仲要早起身返工<br />\n<br />\n一到放假日子，好自然就唔想早起身<br />\n有得瞓晏啲就梗係瞓晏啲<br />\nHea下hea下又會過左個假期<br />\n其實我好撚憎星期日，因為我知道黎緊嗰5日又要做狗<br />\n<br />\n有時都唔知自己係生存緊定生活緊<br />\n我仲記得激戰張家輝嗰陣講過「我唔想到熄燈嗰陣，連一件值得回憶嘅事都無」<br />\n我好怕自己咁樣就會過左成世人<br />\n有無人有同感"},{"pid":"138f70d52654b81ceccce229108097b127fa7258","tid":751783,"uid":10895,"like":7,"dislike":4,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T07:41:50.000Z","msg":"由讀小學開始到做野都唔鐘意星期日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0af03f06e05fd725c92ba8e1be9575cd312b23ee","tid":751783,"uid":19978,"like":17,"dislike":8,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T07:44:10.000Z","msg":"五天工作仲想點"},{"pid":"f46ea97f5cc18f74253904b6d79564043d6f2d34","tid":751783,"uid":191450,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T07:46:03.000Z","msg":"屌 你揀㗎大佬<br />\n要做一早做咗 仲使開post?"},{"pid":"15cfe3caa2ade0f8037f54d337cc0a6ff766ebcb","tid":751783,"uid":107419,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T07:46:30.000Z","msg":"等待上進撚全面進場。"},{"pid":"6552bff9384ecd031c54e267a5aa4843a5525922","tid":751783,"uid":102096,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T07:46:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e880f7101acd5fdf304edb287f78fc68a08caabe","tid":751783,"uid":107419,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T07:48:09.000Z","msg":"鬥慘撚已經進場。"},{"pid":"460acb33fa241345678acca35d99b7657c1f3815","tid":751783,"uid":125079,"like":11,"dislike":3,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T07:52:53.000Z